Add Employee: POST /employees/add

{
  "empName": "John Doe",
  "department": "IT",
  "baseLocation": "Bangalore"
}

Edit Employee: PUT /employees/edit

{
  "empId": 1,
  "empName": "John Doe",
  "department": "Finance",
  "baseLocation": "Mumbai"
}

Search Employee: GET /employees/search/1
View All Employees: GET /employees/view-all
Remove Employee: DELETE /employees/remove/1